<section class="principles-section" id="principles">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row justify-content-center no-gutters mb-5">
            <div class="col-xl-6 col-lg-8">
                <div class="text-center">
                    <h2>Guiding Principles</h2>
                    <p class="mb-0">Excellence in AI and engineering requires more than technical skills.
                        These principles guide how I work and deliver exceptional results.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="row reveal">
            <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6 mb-4">
                <div class="principle">
                    <div class="project-text">
                        <h4>Be cool</h4>
                        <p>Exceptional people are neither ordinary nor dull. They strive to find a niche for their
                            unique abilities and work to inspire others.</p>
                        <figure class="mb-0">
                            <blockquote class="blockquote">
                                <p class="mb-0">If you've gotta think about being cool, you ain't cool.</p>
                            </blockquote>
                            <figcaption class="blockquote-footer">Keith Richards</figcaption>
                        </figure>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6 mb-4">
                <div class="principle">
                    <div class="project-text">
                        <h4>Move fast</h4>
                        <p>Exceptional people focus on progressing towards set business goals in small
                            iterations. This allows them to be flexible and change direction where needed while keeping
                            a sporty, enduring pace.</p>
                        <figure class="mb-0">
                            <blockquote class="blockquote">
                                <p class="mb-0">The first principle is that you must not fool yourself — and you are
                                    the easiest person to fool.</p>
                            </blockquote>
                            <figcaption class="blockquote-footer">Richard Feynman</figcaption>
                        </figure>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6 mb-4">
                <div class="principle">
                    <div class="project-text">
                        <h4>Balance</h4>
                        <p>Exceptional people know that almost every hard decision is an act of
                            balance. That's why we ride the wave.</p>
                        <figure class="mb-0">
                            <blockquote class="blockquote">
                                <p class="mb-0">Life is like riding a bicycle. To keep your balance, you must keep
                                    moving.</p>
                            </blockquote>
                            <figcaption class="blockquote-footer">Albert Einstein</figcaption>
                        </figure>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6 mb-4">
                <div class="principle">
                    <div class="project-text">
                        <h4>Elevate quality</h4>
                        <p>Exceptional people have very high standards. They shape high-quality
                            products, services and processes with exceptional, often unexpected quality.</p>
                        <figure class="mb-0">
                            <blockquote class="blockquote">
                                <p class="mb-0">My tastes are simple: I am easily satisfied with the best.</p>
                            </blockquote>
                            <figcaption class="blockquote-footer">Sir Winston S. Churchill</figcaption>
                        </figure>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6 mb-4">
                <div class="principle">
                    <div class="project-text">
                        <h4>Always learn</h4>
                        <p>Exceptional people are never done learning and always seek self-improvement.</p>
                        <figure class="mb-0">
                            <blockquote class="blockquote">
                                <p class="mb-0">There is only one good—knowledge, and one evil—ignorance.</p>
                            </blockquote>
                            <figcaption class="blockquote-footer">Socrates</figcaption>
                        </figure>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6 mb-4">
                <div class="principle">
                    <div class="project-text">
                        <h4>Build trust</h4>
                        <p>Exceptional people are honest with themselves and others. They value the
                            strength of people's relationships over robustness of systems. They try to be helpful,
                            instead of trying to be right.</p>
                        <figure class="mb-0">
                            <blockquote class="blockquote">
                                <p class="mb-0">People don't care how much you know until they know how much you
                                    care.</p>
                            </blockquote>
                            <figcaption class="blockquote-footer">John C. Maxwell</figcaption>
                        </figure>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

    </div>
</section>
